            <li><a href="https://id.theguardian.com/signout?returnUrl=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2013/dec/09/recovering-stolen-bitcoin-sheep-marketplace-trading-digital-currency-money">Sign out</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

